OL,3,CSt David's Hall could remain shut a
OL,4,Cyear longer than expected
OL,6,FCardiff's St David's Hall could be
OL,7,Fclosed for months longer than expected.
OL,9,FThe city's main classical music venue,
OL,10,Fwhich needs to have its roof replaced
OL,11,Fdue to reinforced autoclaved aerated
OL,12,Fconcrete (RAAC), was originally
OL,13,Fexpected to remain closed until 2025.
OL,15,FHowever as a listed building, it needs
OL,16,Fextra consent prior to works and this
OL,17,Fhas not been obtained yet meaning the
OL,18,Fhall might not reopen until 2026.
