OL,3,CSt David's Hall could remain shut a
OL,4,Cyear longer than expected
OL,6,FCardiff Council said it understands
OL,7,FAcademy Music Group (AMG), which
OL,8,Fsigned an agreement for a lease to
OL,9,Ftake on the running of St David's Hall
OL,10,Fin April 2024, is preparing an
OL,11,Fapplication and at this stage, it
OL,12,Fcannot confirm how long works will
OL,13,Ftake.
OL,15,FAt the most recent full council
OL,16,Fmeeting, leader of the Liberal
OL,17,FDemocrats group at Cardiff Council,
OL,18,FCllr Rodney Berman, asked for a
OL,19,Fprogress update on the venue.
