OL,3,CSt David's Hall could remain shut a
OL,4,Cyear longer than expected
OL,6,FThe council's cabinet member for
OL,7,Fculture, sports and parks, Cllr
OL,8,FJennifer Burke, said the listing of
OL,9,Fthe building has "significantly
OL,10,Fprolonged the process" of its repair
OL,11,Fand it is anticipated that work could
OL,12,Ftake 18 months to complete once all
OL,13,Fplanning permissions are secured.
OL,15,FAn inspection at St David's Hall last
OL,16,Fyear found that the roof would need to
OL,17,Fbe completely replaced due to the
OL,18,Fcondition of panels in the ceiling.
