OL,3,CSt David's Hall could remain shut a
OL,4,Cyear longer than expected
OL,6,FExperts were brought in to look at St
OL,7,FDavid's Hall after health and safety
OL,8,Fguidance changed on RAAC.
OL,10,FThe material is a type of lightweight
OL,11,Fconcrete which is prone to sudden
OL,12,Ffailure as it ages and is found to
OL,13,Fhave a limited lifespan.
OL,15,FCllr Berman said he was disappointed
OL,16,Fto learn that the re-opening of St
OL,17,FDavid's Hall is further off than what
OL,18,Fwas initially expected.
