OL,6,FHe said: "Since closing in September
OL,7,F2023 we are yet to even see a start to
OL,8,Fany works being undertaken to start
OL,9,Ffixing the roof of St David's Hall.
OL,11,F"This is creating significant delays
OL,12,Fand forcing the cancellation of
OL,13,Fimportant cultural events such as the
OL,14,FBBC Cardiff Singer of the World
OL,15,Fcompetition that was due to take place
OL,16,Fin 2025.
