OL,3,CSt David's Hall could remain shut a
OL,4,Cyear longer than expected
OL,6,FAt a Cardiff Council governance and
OL,7,Faudit committee meeting held in July,
OL,8,Fa senior officer at the council said
OL,9,Fthere were no concerns about the
OL,10,Ftiming of repair works at St David's
OL,11,FHall after Cllr Berman raised the same
OL,12,Fissue of a lack of repair work there.
OL,14,FIn a recent statement, Cllr Jennifer
OL,15,FBurke said: "The council understands
OL,16,Fthat AMG has completed its survey and
OL,17,Fis preparing an application for the
OL,18,Fworks.
OL,20,F"At this stage we cannot say for sure
OL,21,Fhow long the works might take.
